data.title: Who Is Kris Jenner Dating? Boyfriend Corey Gamble’s Age & Job
data.meta_description: Many fans are curious to know more about Kris Jenner's boyfriend, Corey Gamble. Here's everything you need to know.
data.meta_site_name: ComingSoon.net - Movie Trailers, TV & Streaming News, and More
data.text:
Fans of Keeping Up With the Kardashians, and now The Kardashians, are familiar with Kris Jenner‘s partner, Corey Gamble. However, many viewers who are new to the show often have many questions about Gamble regarding who he is, what his age is, and what he does.

Here’s everything you need to know about Kris Jenner’s boyfriend, Corey Gamble.

Who is Kris Jenner dating in 2024?

Kris Jenner is currently dating Corey Gamble.

They started their relationship in August 2014 after meeting at fashion designer Riccardo Tisci’s 40th birthday party in Ibiza, Spain, where Gamble was working as Justin Bieber‘s tour manager. At the time, Jenner was in the process of divorcing her previous partner to whom she had been married for 22 years.

Recently, the KUWTK star posted a picture on Instagram celebrating Valentine’s Day. The caption reads, “My Valentine!!!!! I love you @coreygamble ❤️?❤️?”

What is Corey Gamble’s age?

Corey Gamble, a native of Atlanta, Georgia, is 43 years old.

Kris Jenner’s partner, Corey Gamble, defies the age gap. At 43, he’s 25 years younger than Kris, and incredibly, just one month older than her daughter, Kim Kardashian. Despite the unconventional age difference, their relationship has thrived for years. According to People, after graduating from Westlake High School in 1999, Gamble pursued business marketing at Morehouse College.

What job does Corey Gamble do for a living?

Corey Gamble is employed as a talent manager within the music industry.

He notably served as Justin Bieber’s tour manager and has collaborated with numerous other renowned artists. In his role, he maintains associations with prominent figures such as hospitality entrepreneur David Grutman and Hillsong pastor Carl Lentz.
